                    },
                    "effect": "You twist the gem along the blade corresponding with the desired weapon property rune: red for flaming, blue for frost, or yellow for shock. You take 1d6 damage of the type the chosen rune deals. You can instead twist the black gem to disable the active property rune, taking no damage.",
